name: Mohammed Ait Lahcen
body:
### Welcome.
I'm a PhD student in economics at the University of Basel where I'm part of the [Economic Theory research group](https://wwz.unibas.ch/en/faculty/home/abteilung/witheo/). My main research interests are:
* Monetary economics
* Labor economics
* Search and matching theory
* Computational economics
